1.0.2

Database changes
----------------
We changed two feilds in the database table intro_page from TINYINT(3) to INT(3)
You need to do this.

mysql> ALTER TABLE intro_page MODIFY toppos INT(3);
mysql> ALTER TABLE intro_page MODIFY leftpos INT(3);
mysql> ALTER TABLE intro_page ADD color varchar(6) NOT NULL DEFAULT '333333' AFTER leftpos;
mysql> ALTER TABLE intro_page ADD bgcolor varchar(6) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'FFFFFF' AFTER color;
mysql> ALTER TABLE intro_page ADD opacity TINYINT(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '5' AFTER background;


